{"tid":2011583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外界憂口罩銅物料被吸入人體 薛永恒相信不會發生","createTime":"2020-05-11T05:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T08:55:42.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"89c2120063129d375a6ee6425ae66159559a566a","tid":2011583,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:56:01.000Z","msg":"外界憂口罩銅物料被吸入人體 薛永恒相信不會發生<br />\n2020-05-11 HKT 12:13<br />\n<br />\n政府今日起向市民派遞銅芯抗疫口罩，估計每日可派十多萬個。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒表示，聽到外界擔心口罩的銅物料脫落被吸入人體，當局正與原材料供應商確認，但相信應不會發生此情況。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有安老業界人士說，雖然已收到政府派發的銅芯抗疫口罩，但院舍人多，如要逐個清洗及晾乾布口罩，有一定困難。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525425-20200511.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525425-20200511.htm&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnycbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=bddaa606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525425-20200511.htm&h=f66922a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525425-20200511.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5ca726a00c83a104f50263588cce115c89695ecc","tid":2011583,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"091c9427415c6fdb8d37f75c3a9728246bf446b9","tid":2011583,"uid":78470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"你話唔會就唔會啊"},{"pid":"dd014f819ac35740e3a2b526a2e47996b53bcd10"